{"tid":417791,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中超女球迷被保安圍毆 唔除衫唔准走","createTime":"2017-09-29T04:13:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-29T05:53:53.000Z","uid":39464,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"344acd17b42b9ca6ecf65996f31d0566bfbaf187","tid":417791,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T04:13:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170929/large/1506656313_7cce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170929%2Flarge%2F1506656313_7cce.jpg&h=beac26af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n周四中超聯賽，天津權健作客江蘇蘇寧以0:1落敗，客隊球迷輸波失望之餘，賽後更慘被保安圍毆。據微博「天津權健助威團」發佈的圖文，多名權健球迷在事件中受傷。<br />\n<br />\n有網民指，事發原因是江蘇主場的保安人員，要求權健球迷脫掉身上球衣才可離開，但是不少女球迷都沒有準備可更換的衣服，因而遭到保安阻撓，以及勒令脫衣，繼而爆發衝突。<br />\n<br />\n不過現場保安人員則另有說法，表示在比賽之前，南京奧體中心安保方面已經與權健球迷代表溝通，並就離場穿著服裝達成一致竟見，賽後基本上所有客隊球迷都脫掉權健球衣離場，只有為數十多名球迷不聽從指示，情緒激動並向保安揮拳，要現場人員將他們隔離。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57269723&amp;category_guid=7032049&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170929\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57269723%26category_guid%3D7032049%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170929&d=eC7lwv5JXOJSk2T6jyClZYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=e0d2a30c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57269723%26category_guid%3D7032049%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170929&h=91b64ca4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57269723&amp;category_guid=7032049&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170929</a>"},{"pid":"c4c65e351af6808200fd9d894edcd09c7545e94d","tid":417791,"uid":49392,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T04:16:10.000Z","msg":"日本av都無咁既情節"},{"pid":"f0571c2aa86e43485bad4865f485f8e9c65fec89","tid":417791,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09